Classification: Mini-Series
Genre: Comedy | Lifestyle
Status: New Series
Network: Sky Atlantic ( United Kingdom)
Airs: Mondays at 10:00 pm
Runtime: 30 Minutes
Premiere: August 27, 2012

Hunderby is a comedy series written by and starring Julia Davis. It is set during the 1800s and focuses on a shipwreck survivor washed ashore near a tiny English village.
